Build-Depends: beancount, debhelper-compat (= 13), dh-sequence-python3, pybuild-plugin-pyproject, python3, python3-beancount, python3-dateutil, python3-pytest <!nocheck>, python3-requests
Description: Price quotes fetcher for Beancount Beanprice is a daily price quotes fetch library for plain-text accounting. It provides a script to fetch market data prices from various sources on the internet and render them for plain text accounting price syntax (and Beancount). . This used to be located within Beancount itself (at v2) under beancount.prices. This repo will contain all future updates to that script and to those price sources.
